Quickstrike/Terrorsaur:





Quickstrike sighed and walked towards Stingtra. The smell of food brought 
him out of his anger enough to get him modivated. He heard the flapping of 
Terrorsaur's wings when he approached her. And at the corner of his eyes, he 
could see the dactyl going for the meat that was set for him.

He wasn't going to have it. The instant the red dactyl came in arms length, 
Quickstrike threw his arm out and stuck his head. Terrorsaur's long beak 
missed. He sqwaked from the hit, and flew towards the outside of the cave, 
grumbling.

"Beat ya to it!" the young Fuzor snapped at the dactyl, mocking him. "Go get 
yer own!" He laughed in a victorious way. "Did ya see that?" he said to 
Stingtra. He was just too proud of himself.

He transformed to his beast mode and snatched the meat up. He crawled away 
from Stingtra and went to a place where he could eat.
